    <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="article" href="https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2020/7/1/21310225/samsung-galaxy-note-20-ultra-leaked-pictures-photos-renders">The Galaxy Note 20 Ultra seemingly just leaked on Samsungs own website</a></h2>
    
    
    
      
