    <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="article" href="https://www.theverge.com/21310442/tv-streaming-youtube-fubo-price-increases-carrier-fees-disputes-costs-cable-television">There are more streaming choices than ever  why are prices going up?</a></h2>
    
    
    
      
